# Git commit authorship policy

For this repository, never add any `Co-authored-by:` trailer to commit messages.

In particular, never add:

`Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>`

All commits must be authored and committed only under the repository local Git identity:

- user.name: ThiagoNobren
- user.email: 38018912+ThiagoNobren@users.noreply.github.com

When asked to commit, use commit messages without co-author trailers.
